ial cost that does not", "bbox": [143.8, 1260.8, 1094.2, 1281.6]}, {"text": "exceed its related reserve. With respect to these reserves, the Company’s income tax expense would include (i) any", "bbox": [143.8, 1285.9, 1094.3, 1306.7]}, {"text": "changes in tax reserves arising from material changes during the period in the facts and circumstances (i.e., new", "bbox": [143.8, 1310.8, 1094.3, 1331.6]}, {"text": "information) surrounding a tax issue and (ii) any difference from the Company’s tax position as recorded in the", "bbox": [143.8, 1335.8, 1094.1, 1356.7]}, {"text": "financial statements and the final resolution of a tax issue during the period.", "bbox": [143.8, 1360.9, 798.2, 1381.7]}, {"text": "Unrecognized tax benefits represent the aggregate tax effect of differences between tax return positions and the", "bbox": [168.8, 1398.3, 1094.1, 1419.2]}, {"text": "amounts otherwise recognized in the Company’s financial statements, and are reflected in “Income taxes payable”", "bbox": [143.8, 1423.4, 1094.0, 1444.2]}, {"text": "101", "bbox": [603.4, 1478.2, 634.7, 1499.0]}]}